-Harbour-Mens/b/43426030 |title=Blue Harbour : Men's : Marks & Spencer |publisher=Marksandspencer.com |accessdate=2011-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111118022717/http://www.marksandspencer.com/Blue-Harbour-Mens/b/43426030 |archive-date=18 November 2011 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| Blue Harbour || Heritage|| Men || Britain's largest men's casual brand|| \u2013\n|-\n| Blue Harbour || Luxury  ||  Men|| Higher-end casual clothing|| \u2013\n|-\n| Blue Harbour || Golf  ||  Men || Golf clothing || \u2013\n|}\n\n'''Blue Harbour''' is Britain's largest men's casuals brand, and includes the sub-brands Heritage, Luxury and Golf.\n\n==Other clothing lines==\n\n===Other adult only clothes lines===\nM&S markets its miscellaneous and specialist adult clothes ranges under the following product ranges:\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Brand!! Line!!Customer gender!! Products!!Source(s)\n|-\n| Sportsware || \u2013 ||Female|| Casual feminine sportswear|| <ref name=\"ReferenceB\">{{cite web |url=http://www.marksandspencer.com/Sportswear-Womens/b/43118030?ie=UTF8&intid=gnav_women_sportswear&ie=UTF8 |title=Sportswear : Women's : Marks & Spencer |publisher=Marksandspencer.com |accessdate=2011-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100527053022/http://www.marksandspencer.com/Sportswear-Womens/b/43118030?ie=UTF8&intid=gnav_women_sportswear&ie=UTF8 |archive-date=27 May 2010 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.marksandspencer.com/Tops-Sportswear-Womens/b/72149031 |title=Tops : Sportswear : Women's : Marks & Spencer |publisher=Marksandspencer.com |accessdate=2011-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101010033022/http://www.marksandspencer.com/Tops-Sportswear-Womens/b/72149031 |archive-date=10 October 2010 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| Bridal (only available online) || \u2013 || Female || Wedding clothes || \u2013\n|-\n| Love Life, love leisure || \u2013 || Female || Casual feminine sportswear||-\n|-\n| Petite Collection (selecte