rmal luxury'''\n* Thermal luxury \u2013 unisex thermals<ref name=\"marksandspencer.com\"/>\n\n'''Ultimate'''\n* Ultimate \u2013 women's socks and hosiery<ref name=\"auto5\"/>\n\n'''Adored'''\n* Adored \u2013 sexy, specialist and thermal women's socks and hosiery, but merged with Ultimate in 2012<ref name=\"auto5\"/>\n\n'''Katy Livingston'''\n* Katy Livingston \u2013 upmarket sports clothes and merchandise relating to the British athlete [[Katy Livingston]]\n\n'''The Zandra Rhodes collection'''\n* The Zandra Rhodes collection \u2013 upmarket woollen clothes modelled and made by the British fashion designer [[Zandra Rhodes]], [[Order of the British Empire|CBE]]/[[Royal Designers for Industry|RDI]] <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-1170265/M-S-pink-bring-eccentric-designer-Zandra-Rhodes-board-bold-new-collection.html|title=M&S back in the pink as they bring eccentric designer Zandra Rhodes on board with bold new collection|publisher=}}</ref>\n\n'''Party, Party, Party!'''\n* Party, Party, Party! \u2013 seasonal party clothes; reduced to women's wear in 2012<ref name=\"auto3\">{{cite web |url=http://www.marksandspencer.com/Partywear-Womenswear/b/303151031?ie=UTF8&intid=gnav_women_partywear&pf_rd_r=1ZA1BMCE03TW2KMV38ZQ&pf_rd_m=A2BO0OYVBKIQJM&pf_rd_t=201&pf_rd_i=B001UGVA16&pf_rd_p=473397593&pf_rd_s=global-top-8 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130128123519/http://www.marksandspencer.com/Partywear-Womenswear/b/303151031?ie=UTF8&intid=gnav_women_partywear&pf_rd_r=1ZA1BMCE03TW2KMV38ZQ&pf_rd_m=A2BO0OYVBKIQJM&pf_rd_t=201&pf_rd_i=B001UGVA16&pf_rd_p=473397593&pf_rd_s=global-top-8 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2013-01-28 |title=Partywear : Womenswear : Marks & Spencer |publisher=Marksandspencer.com |date= |accessdate=2009-11-07 }}</ref>\n\n'''Breakthrough Breast Cancer'''\n*M&S periodically markets charitable ''Love Pink'' clothes for [[Breakthrough Breast Cancer]]. M&S has sold a wide range of charitable women's clothes for Breakthrough Breast Cancer<ref name=\"breakthrough.org.uk\">[http://breakthrough.org.uk/our_work/ftbc/fashion_targets.html ] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101120134800/http://breakthrough.org.uk/our_work/ftbc/fashion_targets.html |date=20 November 2010 }}</ref> for many years.\n\n'''Essential'''\n* Essential \u2013 upmarket skirts and T-shirts (merged into Portfolio, along with Perfect)\n\n'''Plus range maternity'''\n* Plus range maternity \u2013 large stores only; merged with Limited Collection Maternity as 'M&S Maternity'\n\n'''Limited Collection Maternity''' \n* Limited Collection Maternity \u2013 merged with Plus Range Maternity as 'M&S Maternity'\n\n'''Tailoring'''\n* Tailoring \u2013 formal shirts, ties, and formal accessories\n\n'''Floor 1 discount brands'''\n* Floor 1 discount brands \u2013 women's discount fashion clothes (replaced by the 'Designer discount' line)\n\n===Other children's only clothes===\nM&S markets its miscellaneous and specialist childrenswear under the following brand names:\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Brand!! Line!!Customer gender!! Products!!Source(s)\n|-\n| Skiware || \u2013 || [[Unisex]] || Children's ski wear||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marksandspencer.com/Skiwear-Kids/b/323080031?ie=UTF8&pf_rd_r=099X3X4K5KQT56SJP9CW&pf_rd_m=A2BO0OYVBKIQJM&pf_rd_t=101&pf_rd_i=53882031&pf_rd_p=475115433&pf_rd_s=left-nav-2 |title=Marks & Spencer |publisher=Marksandspencer.com |date= |accessdate=2011-07-18 }}{{dead link|date=May 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n|-\n| Essential-Value-Essential-Quality || \u2013 || [[Unisex]] || Children's cheap, utilitarian 'good value' clothes ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marksandspencer.com/Essential-Value-Essential-Quality-Older-Boys-6-14-yrs-Kids/b/598252031?intid=Engage_mod_1_0 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130128111334/http://www.marksandspencer.com/Essential-Value-Essential-Quality-Older-Boys-6-14-yrs-Kids/b/598252031?intid=Engage_mod_1_0 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2013-0