It was founded in 1965 and is one of the oldest schools in [[Vinayagapuram, Sri Lanka]].The school provides both [[Primary education|Primary]] and [[Secondary education]].\n\n==Principals==\n*Mr.K.Subramaniam (1965-1968)\n*Mr.S.T.Pupalaretnam(1968-1971)\n*Mr.J.S.Nadarajah(1971-1974)\n*Mr.S.K.Rajendram(1974-1979)\n*Mr.M.Sellappa(1979-1980)\n*Mr.V.Sathasivam(1980-1994)\n*Mr.K.Ganesamoorthy(1994-1997)\n*Mr.P.Navaretnam(1997-1999)\n*Mr.E.Velupillai(1999-2001)\n*Mr.S.Dhavarasa(2001-2006)\n*Mr.S.Pethambaram(2006-2008)\n*Mr.K.Sriskandarasa(2008-2010)\n*Mr.S.Paranjothi(2010-2014)\n*Mr.R.M.Anton(2014-2018)\n\n==School Anthem==\n[[File:School_anthem.jpg|thumb|right]]\n\n==References==\n\n{{Uncategorized|date=April 2020}}\n", "text_old": "{{Proposed deletion/dated\n  |concern = Fails [[WP:NSCHOOL]], requires significant coverage in multiple independent reliable secondary sources]].\n  |timestamp = 20200408075425\n  |help = off\n}}\n{{Multiple issues|\n{{Notability|Places|date=April 2020}}\n{{More citations needed|date=April 2020}}\n}}\n{{Infobox school\n|name                   = Vinayagapuram maha vidyalayam,Thirukkovil\n|native_name            = {{lang|ta|\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bbe \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd, \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd }}\n|logo                   = \n|seal_image             = \n|image                  = Vinayagapuram_maha_vidyalayam.jpg\n|image_size             = \n|alt                    = \n|caption                = School entrance\n|motto                  = '''Knowledge is personality'''\n|motto_translation      = {{lang|ta|\u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc7 \u0b86\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc8}} \n|streetaddress          = Central road,\n|location               = [[Vinayagapuram, Sri Lanka]]\n|region                 = \n|city                   = [[Thirukkovil]]\n|state                  = [[Ampara]]\n|province        